         <Description>This dataset contains spin resolution measurements of the electron drift velocity
            and electric field with GOOD/CAUTION qualities from the EDI experiment on the Cluster C3 spacecraft. 
            These data have been converted into Cluster Exchange Format from the orignal Cluster Science Data System 
            Common Data Format (CDF) Prime Parameter files that were made available through the Cluster Science Data System. 
            The SPIN dataset is identical to the PP dataset but without chi_squared variable.
         </Description>
